    "name": "爱开盖乐世 Arcade Galaxy",
    "steam_appid": 3090620,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到《爱开盖乐世 Arcade Galaxy》！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款充满创意与挑战的派对闯关游戏中，你将操控名叫「卡波」的可爱动物车车，突破一道道精心设计的玩家自制关卡。地图上那些旋转杆、地雷、大锤子，是无数“整活高手”精心布置的障碍，他们可不会让你轻松通关！但别担心，好好利用加速垫、弹跳板、喷射冲刺等机关道具，在闯关中脱颖而出，刷新你的最佳成绩！在多人模式中，你还可以选择使用独特技能，比如雷击、超级跳跃等，电晕对手、飞跃陷阱，告诉其他玩家——谁才是这个宇宙最强的存在！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/fccd61c525ce7046e5c8221cfabd39da.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/fccd61c525ce7046e5c8221cfabd39da.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/fccd61c525ce7046e5c8221cfabd39da.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了刺激的竞速体验，游戏还内置了一套功能强大的关卡编辑器。你可以自由创作和定制几乎游戏中的一切元素：从地形方块、机关陷阱，到物体的行为逻辑，尽情释放你的脑洞，让创意照进现实。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/08e419525e86c5712670464cdd1e34f4.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/08e419525e86c5712670464cdd1e34f4.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/08e419525e86c5712670464cdd1e34f4.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关卡创作完成后，你可以将它上传分享，邀请全球玩家挑战你的杰作。从设置巧妙陷阱、构造奇葩机制，到打造属于你个人风格的专属地图——这一切都由你掌控！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/24eede67dd3a18c6b98a5d7c8aeecfce.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/24eede67dd3a18c6b98a5d7c8aeecfce.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/24eede67dd3a18c6b98a5d7c8aeecfce.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《爱开盖乐世 Arcade Galaxy》中，你还能根据自己的喜好定制卡波的造型和技能。丰富的外观与能力搭配，帮助你打造独一无二的个性卡波，展现你的专属风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/82aff679a8634040bce59601439e2647.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/82aff679a8634040bce59601439e2647.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/82aff679a8634040bce59601439e2647.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创造、分享、挑战——现在就加入宇宙闯关大冒险，和全世界的玩家一起分享你的灵感与热情，体验无穷无尽的创作乐趣！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>无限挑战</strong>：海量玩家自制地图，等你打破记录、挑战极限，或与好友一决高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/7a7174054727a3f24690d361519c493c.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/7a7174054727a3f24690d361519c493c.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/7a7174054727a3f24690d361519c493c.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠 <strong>打造你的幻想世界</strong>：使用强大编辑工具，自定义地图中的每一个细节，从地形布局到玩法机制，应有尽有。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/304952a8010f1c560e1f8baa9e416fcb.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/304952a8010f1c560e1f8baa9e416fcb.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/304952a8010f1c560e1f8baa9e416fcb.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>全球分享</strong>：发布你的作品，邀请全世界的玩家来征服你的专属关卡！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/81805177c4b3bdd9394f8855e9711a24.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/81805177c4b3bdd9394f8855e9711a24.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/81805177c4b3bdd9394f8855e9711a24.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎨 <strong>个性定制卡波</strong>：通过外观与技能的自由组合，打造专属于你的卡波，成为游戏中的个性化代表！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/98ca7e8bf5f63aa065530be24af0d018.poster.avif?t=1768142077\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/98ca7e8bf5f63aa065530be24af0d018.webm?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/98ca7e8bf5f63aa065530be24af0d018.mp4?t=1768142077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>快来加入我们，一起打造属于你的银河冒险吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090620/extras/827167bf6337d9c0a1b0a583424b2f7d.avif?t=1768142077\" width=200 height=129 /></span></p>",
